{"type":"message","id":"902292ad","parentId":"67b6709d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:02:08.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我创建一个项目结构概览文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bf0520086fad43ff9856a50f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 基础资料服务 - 项目结构\n\n```\nTianyou.BasicDataService/\n│\n├── Controllers/                    # API控制器层\n│   ├── DepartmentController.cs     # 部门管理API\n│   ├── PositionController.cs      # 岗位管理API\n│   ├── EmployeeController.cs      # 员工管理API\n│   ├── CustomerController.cs      # 客户管理API\n│   ├── SupplierController.cs      # 供应商管理API\n│   ├── MaterialController.cs      # 物料管理API\n│   └── WarehouseController.cs     # 仓库管理API\n│\n├── Entities/                       # 数据实体层\n│   ├── DepartmentEntity.cs        # 部门实体\n│   ├── PositionEntity.cs          # 岗位实体\n│   ├── EmployeeEntity.cs          # 员工实体\n│   ├── CustomerEntity.cs          # 客户实体\n│   ├── SupplierEntity.cs          # 供应商实体\n│   ├── MaterialEntity.cs          # 物料实体\n│   ├── WarehouseEntity.cs         # 仓库实体\n│   └── WarehouseStockEntity.cs    # 库存实体\n│\n├── Models/                         # DTO模型层\n│   └── BasicDataModels.cs         # 所有DTO模型\n│       ├── DepartmentDto\n│       ├── PositionDto\n│       ├── EmployeeDto\n│       ├── CustomerDto\n│       ├── SupplierDto\n│       ├── MaterialDto\n│       ├── WarehouseDto\n│       └── WarehouseStockDto\n│\n├── Repositories/                   # 数据仓储层\n│   └── BasicDataRepository.cs     # 基础数据仓储\n│       ├── Department CRUD (6个方法)\n│       ├── Position CRUD (6个方法)\n│       ├── Employee CRUD (6个方法)\n│       ├── Customer CRUD (6个方法)\n│       ├── Supplier CRUD (6个方法)\n│       ├── Material CRUD (6个方法)\n│       ├── Warehouse CRUD (6个方法)\n│       └── WarehouseStock (3个方法)\n│\n├── Services/                       # 业务服务层\n│   └── BasicDataService.cs        # 基础数据服务\n│       ├── Department 服务 (7个方法)\n│       ├── Position 服务 (7个方法)\n│       ├── Employee 服务 (7个方法)\n│       ├── Customer 服务 (7个方法)\n│       ├── Supplier 服务 (7个方法)\n│       ├── Material 服务 (7个方法)\n│       ├── Warehouse 服务 (7个方法)\n│       └── WarehouseStock 服务 (1个方法)\n│\n├── Program.cs                      # 应用入口\n├── appsettings.json               # 配置文件\n├── Dockerfile                     # Docker部署文件\n├── README.md                      # 服务说明文档\n└── API_TEST_GUIDE.md             # API测试指南\n\n```\n\n## 层级关系\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│        Controllers (API层)           │\n│  处理HTTP请求，返回JSON响应          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                 ↓\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│        Services (业务逻辑层)        │\n│  业务规则、DTO转换、事务管理        │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                 ↓\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│      Repositories (数据访问层)      │\n│  数据库操作、SQL执行、结果映射      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n                 ↓\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│        Entities (数据实体层)        │\n│  数据表映射、业务规则、校验         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## 数据流\n\n### 1. 读取数据流程\n```\nHTTP GET Request\n    ↓\nController → Service → Repository → Database\n    ↓\nEntity → DTO → JSON Response\n```\n\n### 2. 创建数据流程\n```\nHTTP POST Request\n    ↓\nJSON → Controller → Service\n    ↓\nDTO → Entity → Repository → Database\n    ↓\nCreated Response\n```\n\n### 3. 更新数据流程\n```\nHTTP PUT Request\n    ↓\nJSON → Controller → Service\n    ↓\nDTO → Entity → Repository → Database\n    ↓\nUpdated Response\n```\n\n### 4. 删除数据流程\n```\nHTTP DELETE Request\n    ↓\nController → Service → Repository → Database\n    ↓\nDeleted Response\n```\n\n## 模块依赖\n\n```\nTianyou.BasicDataService\n    │\n    ├── Tianyou.Core.Abstractions (核心抽象)\n    │\n    ├── Tianyou.Data (数据访问)\n    │\n    ├── SqlSugar (ORM框架)\n    │\n    ├── Microsoft.AspNetCore.OpenApi (API文档)\n    │\n    ├── Swashbuckle.AspNetCore (Swagger)\n    │\n    └── Serilog.AspNetCore (日志)\n```\n\n## 技术栈\n\n### 核心框架\n- .NET 10.0\n- ASP.NET Core Web API\n\n### 数据访问\n- SqlSugar 5.1.4.154\n- SQLite\n\n### API文档\n- Swashbuckle.AspNetCore 7.2.0\n- OpenAPI/Swagger 3.0\n\n### 日志\n- Serilog.AspNetCore 8.0.0\n\n### 架构模式\n- DDD (领域驱动设计)\n- 微服务架构\n- 仓储模式 (Repository Pattern)\n\n## 数据库表\n\n### 组织架构\n- `sys_department` (部门表)\n- `sys_position` (岗位表)\n\n### 人员管理\n- `sys_employee` (员工表)\n\n### 客商管理\n- `crm_customer` (客户表)\n- `scm_supplier` (供应商表)\n\n### 物资管理\n- `wms_material` (物料表)\n- `wms_warehouse` (仓库表)\n- `wms_warehouse_stock` (库存表)\n\n## API端点\n\n### RESTful 设计\n- `GET /api/{resource}` - 列表查询\n- `GET /api/{resource}/{id}` - 详情查询\n- `POST /api/{resource}` - 创建资源\n- `PUT /api/{resource}/{id}` - 更新资源\n- `DELETE /api/{resource}/{id}` - 删除资源\n\n### 资源列表\n- `/api/department` - 部门\n- `/api/position` - 岗位\n- `/api/employee` - 员工\n- `/api/customer` - 客户\n- `/api/supplier` - 供应商\n- `/api/material` - 物料\n- `/api/warehouse` - 仓库\n- `/api/warehouse/{id}/stock` - 库存\n\n## 配置说明\n\n### appsettings.json\n```json\n{\n  \"Database\": {\n    \"ConnectionString\": \"Data Source=/path/to/tianyou.db\"\n  },\n  \"Logging\": {\n    \"LogLevel\": {\n      \"Default\": \"Information\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 环境变量\n- `DATABASE_CONNECTION_STRING` - 数据库连接字符串\n- `ASPNETCORE_URLS` - 服务监听URL\n- `ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT` - 运行环境\n\n## 部署选项\n\n### 1. 本地开发\n```bash\ndotnet run\n```\n\n### 2. Docker部署\n```bash\ndocker build -t tianyou-basicdata .\ndocker run -p 5005:5005 tianyou-basicdata\n```\n\n### 3. Docker Compose\n```yaml\nservices:\n  basicdata:\n    image: tianyou-basicdata\n    ports:\n      - \"5005:5005\"\n    volumes:\n      - ./database:/database\n```\n\n### 4. Kubernetes\n```yaml\napiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: tianyou-basicdata\nspec:\n  replicas: 3\n  template:\n    spec:\n      containers:\n      - name: basicdata\n        image: tianyou-basicdata\n        ports:\n        - containerPort: 5005\n```\n\n## 监控和日志\n\n### 健康检查\n- 端点: `/health`\n- 返回: 服务状态和时间戳\n\n### 日志位置\n- 控制台: 实时输出\n- 文件: `logs/basicdata-{date}.log`\n- 滚动: 每天滚动\n\n### 性能指标\n- SQL执行日志\n- 请求响应时间\n- 数据库连接数\n\n## 扩展点\n\n### 1. 添加新实体\n1. 在 `Entities/` 创建实体类\n2. 在 `Models/` 创建DTO类\n3. 在 `Repositories/` 添加仓储方法\n4. 在 `Services/` 添加服务方法\n5. 在 `Controllers/` 创建控制器\n\n### 2. 添加业务逻辑\n1. 在 `Services/` 修改服务方法\n2. 实现业务规则\n3. 添加事务管理\n4. 更新API文档\n\n### 3. 集成其他服务\n1. 添加HTTP客户端\n2. 配置服务发现\n3. 实现API调用\n4. 处理异常\n\n## 最佳实践\n\n### 1. 代码规范\n- 每个函数不超过50行\n- 使用异步方法\n- 完整的XML注释\n- 清晰的命名\n\n### 2. 安全性\n- 参数化查询\n- 输入验证\n- 审计日志\n- 权限控制\n\n### 3. 性能优化\n- 使用异步IO\n- 批量操作\n- 索引优化\n- 缓存策略\n\n### 4. 可维护性\n- 单一职责\n- 依赖注入\n- 配置分离\n- 文档完整\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/services/Tianyou.BasicDataService/PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":42,"output":2220,"cacheRead":42892,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45154,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224104509}}
